  </section>

  <!-- How We Do It -->
  <section class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-16">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full text-center">
        <span class="block text-base text-wr-muted">How do we do it?</span>
        <h2 class="font-medium text-2xl md:text-[32px] leading-tight tracking-[-0.02em] text-wr-dark">
          We combine tools, data, and expertise to find top candidates.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
          <div class="lg:max-w-md w-full lg:mr-auto flex flex-col gap-6">
            <div>
              <p class="text-wr-dark"><strong>Global mindset, local expertise</strong></p>
              <p class="text-wr-muted text-base leading-relaxed">We recruit across Latin America with deep market knowledge, making our searches more precise and globally aligned.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-wr-dark"><strong>Proprietary tools & continuous improvement</strong></p>
              <p class="text-wr-muted text-base leading-relaxed">We develop search and evaluation methodologies to increase speed and accuracy.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-wr-dark"><strong>Better matches, guaranteed</strong></p>
              <p class="text-wr-muted text-base leading-relaxed">We align technical skills, culture and expectations to ensure long-term fit and reduce hiring risk.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="relative w-full max-w-[320px] sm:max-w-[450px] aspect-square">
            <img
              src="https://werecruit.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Frame-1410087959-1.png"
              alt="How we work"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain object-center"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-[#F2F7F9] py-16 md:py-24 -mx-6 px-6" style="margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%); margin-right: calc(-50vw + 50%); width: 100vw;">
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Dot pattern -->
      <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 w-full max-w-[1311px] h-[234px]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#132738 1.5px, transparent 1.5px); background-size: 47px 47px;"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-16 max-w-[860px] mx-auto text-center bg-[#F2F7F9] relative z-10 pt-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full mx-auto text-center">
          <span class="block text-base text-wr-muted">About We Recruit IT</span>
          <h2 class="font-medium text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[56px] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-wr-dark">
            We connect people.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-[#BBC7CC]">
          For more than a decade, we've specialized in understanding LATAM's talent landscape and creating reliable, long-term connections between companies and exceptional engineers.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Team carousel -->
      <div class="max-w-[930px] mx-auto mt-20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bottom-0 w-16 md:w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F2F7F9] to-transparent z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bottom-0 w-16 md:w-32 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#F2F7F9] to-transparent z-10"></div>
        <div class="flex animate-scroll-slow gap-6 items-center" style="width: max-content;">
          <img src="https://werecruit.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Rectangle-51.png" alt="" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-[72px] md:h-[72px] object-cover rounded-xl" />
